==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Supercolumniation
<hw>Su`per*co*lum`ni*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Arch.)</fld> <def>The putting of one order above another; also, an
architectural work produced by this method; <as>as, the putting of the
Doric order in the ground story, Ionic above it, and Corinthian or
Composite above this</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superconception</ent>⟦br⟧
